PART 1: ACTUATOR KYA HAI? (DEFINITION)
--------------------------------------
Definition: Actuator Spring Boot ka ek **Production-Ready Features** ka set hai.
Ye aapke application ki **Monitoring** aur **Management** ke liye ready-made
HTTP endpoints aur MBeans provide karta hai.

Simple Words: Application ki **Health Report** aur **Internal Info** dekhne ka tool.

PART 2: ACTUATOR KYUN USE KARTE HAIN? (USE CASES)
-------------------------------------------------
1. **Health Check:** Kya application chal rahi hai? Database connection alive hai?
2. **Metrics:** Kitne requests aaye? Response time kitna hai? Memory usage kitni hai?
3. **Info:** Application ka version kya hai? Custom build info.
4. **Environment:** `application.properties` ki kaunsi values active hain?
5. **Loggers:** Runtime pe log level change karna (DEBUG se ERROR).
6. **Thread Dump:** Deadlock detect karna.
7. **Heap Dump:** Memory leak analyze karna.

PART 3: DEPENDENCY (pom.xml)
----------------------------
```xml
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-actuator</artifactId>
</dependency>



Default Base Path: /actuator

Endpoint	URL	Kaam (Definition)
health	     /actuator/health	    Application ki current status. UP ya DOWN.
info	     /actuator/info	        Custom application information (version, description).
metrics	     /actuator/metrics	    Performance stats (CPU, Memory, HTTP Requests).
env	         /actuator/env	        Environment properties aur Configuration values.
loggers	      /actuator/loggers	    Runtime pe Log Levels check/change karna.
beans	      /actuator/beans	    Spring Context mein registered saare Beans ki list.
threaddump	 /actuator/threaddump	Sabhi Threads ka snapshot (Deadlock check).
heapdump	 /actuator/heapdump	    Memory ka snapshot (.hprof file download).
mappings	 /actuator/mappings	    Saare @RequestMapping paths ki list.



# 1. Sabhi Endpoints Enable Karna (By Default sirf /health hi open hota hai)
management.endpoints.web.exposure.include=*
# Specific enable karna: health,info,metrics

# 2. Specific Endpoint Disable Karna
management.endpoint.shutdown.enabled=true
management.endpoint.env.enabled=false

# 3. Custom Base Path (Default /actuator hai)
management.endpoints.web.base-path=/monitor

# 4. Port Change Karna (Security: Actuator alag port pe sunega)
management.server.port=8081

# 5. Health Check Mein Details Show Karna (By default sirf Status aata hai)
management.endpoint.health.show-details=always
management.endpoint.health.show-components=always


